# UI and Routing Conventions

- **Routing**: Use React Router declarative APIs: `<BrowserRouter>`, `<Routes>`, `<Route>`, `<Link>`, `useNavigate`, `useLocation`
- **shadcn/ui**: Prefer components from `src/components/ui`; maintain New York style
- **Radix UI**: Use primitive components for accessibility
- **Tailwind v4**: Use CSS variables; co-locate component styles with components
- **Icons**: Import from `lucide-react`
- **Forms**: Use the form primitives in [`src/components/ui/form.tsx`](mdc:src/components/ui/form.tsx)
- **Toasts**: Use [`src/components/ui/sonner.tsx`](mdc:src/components/ui/sonner.tsx)
